<main id="main-content">
<!-- PAGE HERO -->
<header class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div class="page-label">Join the Movement</div>
    <h1>Get <em>Involved</em></h1>
    <p>This campaign runs on grassroots power. No corporate money, no PAC funding — just working people fighting for working people. We need you.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- SIGNATURE COLLECTION URGENCY -->
<section class="sig-banner" aria-label="Ballot signature collection urgency">
  <div class="sig-banner-inner">
    <h2>Priority: Ballot Signatures</h2>
    <p>As an independent candidate, Cortney isn't in the primary. To get on the <strong>November general election ballot</strong>, we need to collect <strong>2,200 valid signatures</strong> and submit them to the Board of Elections by <strong>May 4th, 2026</strong>.</p>
    <p class="small">If you live in Ohio's 11th Congressional District, your signature gets Cortney on the ballot. Volunteer to help canvass for signatures in your neighborhood.</p>
    <div class="sig-banner-footer">
      <p>Not registered to vote yet? You'll need to be registered to sign the petition and to vote in November.</p>
      <a href="voter-registration.html" class="btn-register-vote">Register to Vote →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WAYS TO HELP -->
<section class="ways" aria-labelledby="ways-heading">
  <div class="ways-inner">
    <div class="section-label reveal">How You Can Help</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" id="ways-heading">Every Action <em>Matters</em></h2>
    <p class="section-intro reveal">Change doesn't come from Washington — it comes from communities like ours deciding enough is enough. Here's how you can be part of this movement.</p>

    <div class="ways-grid">
      <a href="#volunteer" class="way-card reveal">
        <span class="way-icon">🚪</span>
        <h3>Canvass</h3>
        <p>Go door-to-door in your neighborhood talking to voters. Face-to-face contact is the most powerful tool in any campaign. We'll train you — no experience needed.</p>
        <span class="way-cta">Volunteer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#volunteer" class="way-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="way-icon">📞</span>
        <h3>Phone Bank</h3>
        <p>Call voters from your home. We provide the script, the list, and the support. If you can make calls, you can phone bank — it's that simple.</p>
        <span class="way-cta">Volunteer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#volunteer" class="way-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="way-icon">📱</span>
        <h3>Digital Organizing</h3>
        <p>Share Cortney's message on social media, write letters to the editor, post in community groups. Digital organizing amplifies our grassroots voice at zero cost.</p>
        <span class="way-cta">Volunteer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#volunteer" class="way-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <span class="way-icon">🪧</span>
        <h3>Yard Signs</h3>
        <p>Yard signs are coming soon. Check the box in the volunteer form below to be first in line when they're ready.</p>
        <span class="way-cta">Volunteer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#volunteer" class="way-card reveal">
        <span class="way-icon">🏠</span>
        <h3>Host a House Party</h3>
        <p>Invite 10 friends to your living room. We'll provide talking points and materials. You provide the space. House parties are how grassroots campaigns win — one conversation at a time.</p>
        <span class="way-cta">Volunteer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="events.html" class="way-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="way-icon">🗓️</span>
        <h3>Attend Events</h3>
        <p>Join us at town halls, rallies, and community events across Cleveland and OH-11. Meet Cortney, meet fellow supporters, and make your voice heard in person.</p>
        <span class="way-cta">See Events →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ site.donateUrl }}" class="way-card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--plum),var(--plum-light));color:white" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="way-icon">💰</span>
        <h3 style="color:white">Donate</h3>
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)">Every dollar from a working person counts more than a corporate PAC check. Small donations power this campaign and send a message that we don't owe anyone anything.</p>
        <span class="way-cta" style="color:var(--coral-light)">Donate Now →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAITH & COMMUNITY -->
<section style="background:var(--cream);padding:4rem 1.5rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05)" id="faith">
  <div style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto">
    <p style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:0.85rem;letter-spacing:0.25em;color:#a0604a;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.75rem">Faith &amp; Community</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3.5vw,2rem);font-weight:900;color:var(--plum);line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Your Church Can Change <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--coral)">This District</em></h2>
    <div style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.8">
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem">Cleveland's Black churches have been the backbone of organizing in this community for generations. From the civil rights movement to today, when change happens in this district, it starts in the pews.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem">Cortney's guiding principle is the Golden Rule — treat others the way you want to be treated. That's not a campaign slogan. It's a moral commitment. And it aligns with what faith communities across Cleveland have been living for decades: care for the sick, feed the hungry, fight for justice, protect the vulnerable.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem"><strong style="color:var(--text)">We're looking for faith leaders and congregations willing to partner with us.</strong> That could mean hosting a candidate forum, sharing voter registration information with your congregation, organizing a signature drive after service, or simply opening a conversation about what Cleveland's families need from their representative.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <a href="#volunteer" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.85rem 2rem;border-radius:10px;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--plum);color:var(--white)">Connect Your Congregation →</a>
        <a href="mailto:cortneyforcongress@gmail.com?subject=Faith%20Community%20Partnership" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.85rem 2rem;border-radius:10px;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase;border:2px solid var(--plum);color:var(--plum)">Email Us Directly</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VOLUNTEER FORM -->
<section class="volunteer-section" id="volunteer" aria-labelledby="volunteer-heading">
  <div class="volunteer-inner">
    <div class="volunteer-intro-aside">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">Volunteer Sign-Up</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:1rem">Join the <em>Team</em></h2>
        <p style="color:var(--text-light);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.8">Fill out the form and we'll reach out with the right opportunities for you. No commitment required.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="volunteer-aside-stat">
        <div class="volunteer-aside-stat-num">100%</div>
        <div class="volunteer-aside-stat-label">Grassroots — no PAC money</div>
      </div>
      <div class="volunteer-aside-stat">
        <div class="volunteer-aside-stat-num">OH-11</div>
        <div class="volunteer-aside-stat-label">Communities we're fighting for</div>
      </div>
      <div class="volunteer-aside-stat">
        <div class="volunteer-aside-stat-num">$0</div>
        <div class="volunteer-aside-stat-label">Corporate donations accepted</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="volunteer-form-col">
    <div class="section-label" style="display:block" aria-hidden="false">Volunteer Sign-Up</div>
    <h2 class="section-title volunteer-form-heading" id="volunteer-heading" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem">Join the <em>Team</em></h2>
    <p class="volunteer-form-intro" style="color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:2.5rem;font-size:1rem">Fill out the form below and we'll reach out with opportunities to get involved. No commitment required — just let us know you're interested.</p>

    <div class="form-card">
      <form name="volunteer" method="POST" action="/success.html" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" id="volunteerForm">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="volunteer">
        <p hidden><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field"></label></p>
        <p class="form-required-note" style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:1.5rem">Fields marked with <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span><span class="sr-only">an asterisk</span> are required.</p>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-group">
            <label for="firstName">First Name <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="firstName" name="first_name" required aria-required="true" autocomplete="given-name">
          </div>
          <div class="field-group">
            <label for="lastName">Last Name <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="lastName" name="last_name" required aria-required="true" autocomplete="family-name">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-group">
          <label for="email">Email Address <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required aria-required="true" autocomplete="email">
        </div>

        <div class="field-group">
          <label for="phone">Phone Number <span style="font-weight:400;color:var(--text-light)">(optional)</span></label>
          <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel">
        </div>

        <div class="field-group">
          <label for="zip">ZIP Code <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="zip" name="zip" required aria-required="true" pattern="[0-9]{5}" maxlength="5" inputmode="numeric" autocomplete="postal-code">
        </div>

        <div class="field-group">
          <label>How would you like to help? <span style="font-weight:400;color:var(--text-light)">(check all that apply)</span></label>
          <ul class="checkbox-list">
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Canvassing"> Canvassing</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Phone Banking"> Phone Banking</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Digital / Social Media"> Digital / Social Media</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Yard Sign"> Yard Sign (coming soon)</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Host a House Party"> Host a House Party</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Event Volunteer"> Event Volunteer</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Donate"> Donate</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Faith Community Leader"> Faith Community Leader</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Data Entry / Admin"> Data Entry / Admin</label></li>
            <li><label><input type="checkbox" name="help[]" value="Other"> Other</label></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="field-group">
          <label for="message">Anything else you'd like us to know? <span style="font-weight:400;color:var(--text-light)">(optional)</span></label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="3" placeholder="Skills, availability, questions — whatever you want to share."></textarea>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Count Me In →</button>
        <p class="form-note">We will never sell or share your information. You can unsubscribe at any time.</p>
      </form>

      <div class="form-success" id="formSuccess" role="alert">
        <h3>You're in! Thank you.</h3>
        <p>We'll be in touch soon with ways to get involved. Keep an eye on your inbox — and in the meantime, spread the word. The more people who know about this campaign, the stronger we get.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem"><strong>Want to do something right now?</strong> Share this page with someone who cares about Ohio's 11th.</p>
      </div>
    </div><!-- end form-card -->
    </div><!-- end volunteer-form-col -->
  </div><!-- end volunteer-inner -->
</section>

